 of the twenty- first century. As evidence the three case studies: i) the cholo-peasantry antimining struggles in Cajamarca
 (Peru) during the 2004 and 2011-2012 against the Newmont Gold Min\-ing Corporation headed in the U.S., ii) the indigenous-peasantry
 mining struggles in Apur}
