 bourgeoisies share the conditions of accumula\-tion for their mutually consented capital concentration and inter-\'93nationalization\'94
 in the period between the 70s and the first decade of the 2000s, with a breaking point in the years 2013-2015, denoting
 a initial disentangle of their rates of profit, that could be extended mildly until 2019, with a recent affirmation between
 2021 and 2023, which supposed to be reinforced with the updated data which considers the 2024 interstate contention. Considering
 its estimation as a proxy to the monetized-capital amount ac\-countable for the exchange of gold-money-capital reserves
 as a reserve fund of surplus\-value congealed under the shape of gold-commodity-capital and gold-money}
